<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.180/a8bfee30ly8hp22ftggynj20go0gomyy.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1724409125&amp;ssig=tPqjxqikUk</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 08:19:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>180</ttl><item><title>[并不简单]#电视剧孤舟# 每次顾易中一摘眼睛，卫的职业病就犯了——不要单手摘眼镜！镜架一变形，镜框一高一低，镜片就不是你的度数了，长期佩戴，近视容易加深....</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[并不简单]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E5%89%A7%E5%AD%A4%E8%88%9F%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E5%89%A7%E5%AD%A4%E8%88%9F%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#电视剧孤舟#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 每次顾易中一摘眼睛，卫的职业病就犯了——&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;不要单手摘眼镜！镜架一变形，镜框一高一低，镜片就不是你的度数了，长期佩戴，近视容易加深......（科普来源：深圳市眼科医院）&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5070481431134269&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;千面狐狸白凤九的微博视频&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br clear=&quot;both&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quo